File to save asIndicatorDirect Linkgdp_per_capita.xlsGDP per capita growth (annual %)NY.GDP.PCAP.KD.ZG
For Debt Data — IMF World Economic Outlook
The government debt variable (government_general_gross_debt_%gdp.xls) comes from the IMF:

Go to → IMF WEO Database
Select "By Countries (all countries)"
In the subject list, select GGXWDG_NGDP (General government gross debt, % of GDP)
Download as Excel → rename file to government_general_gross_debt_%gdp.xls
Place in this data/ folder


How to Download from World Bank (step by step)
For each indicator link above:

Click the link → World Bank indicator page opens
Click "Download" button (top right of the data table)
Select "Excel" format
Save the file in this data/ folder with the exact filename shown above

